**Standard validation pattern (Labs 02-06):**
```
if (startNo < 0) {
    print startNo error
} else if (endNo < 0) {
    print endNo error
} else if (endNo > 9) {
    print endNo too big
} else if (startNo > endNo) {
    print order error
} else {
    // do calculation
}
```

**Loop variants (for loop is always inclusive: i <= endNo):**
- Even: `if (i % 2 == 0) sumEven += i;`
- Odd: `if (i % 2 != 0) sumOdd += i;`
- Squares: `sumSq += (i * i);`
- Cubes: `sumCube = sumCube + (i * i * i);`

